# AVD-KSV-0056: ClusterRole write access to services and ingresses
# Severity: HIGH
# Justification: The github-deployer CI/CD service account must create, update, and delete
# NodePort services and ingresses across dynamically-created feature branch namespaces.
# Namespace-scoped Roles are not feasible because namespaces are created at deploy time
# and the deployer must act before any Role exists in the new namespace.
# Mitigation: Access is restricted to this single service account; audit logging is enabled.
# Review by: 2026-11-11
AVD-KSV-0056
